sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant CL as Client
    participant RX as Receiving node
    participant AP as Applier - owner 1
    participant O2 as Owner 2
    participant O3 as Owner 3

    CL->>RX: Put key, JSON value
    Note over RX: hash key to partition, find owners
    RX->>AP: forward to first healthy owner
    Note over AP: mint dot, apply, durable fsync<br/>no quorum, no peer round-trip
    AP-->>RX: ok
    RX-->>CL: ok - write acknowledged

    Note over AP,O3: asynchronous, after the client is done
    AP-)O2: replicate delta - best effort
    AP-)O3: replicate delta - best effort
    Note over O2,O3: anti-entropy heals anything that was dropped
